snippet.title: Books Alive!
snippet.description:
Popular children's stories brought to life with colour and imagination. Read aloud/read along with some fantastically fun and exciting new and classic kids books. 

ALL ad revenue generated by this channel will go to charities, events and organisations that encourage young people to read. I don’t get paid. Thanks for watching!

Any requests please email booksaliveuk@gmail.com
